LJPC bear with me But I have a working theory that technical analysis is a scam Its a hamster wheel that looks backwards and never can help you in the current moment And only looking backwArds can you see mistakes that it actually makes you continue to make moment to moment The more you fail the more you try to correct based on what the charts look like hours later But in the moment its as if you should do the opposite of what the indicators say and make money by being wrong Im not some salty turd that is upset about losing i do most of my trading on the think or swim paper trade system for practice But Ive been testing this theory the last couple days and its been working marvelously Anyone else see this happen
